<h1><b><b><u>MARCH 2017 -- STATE OF ILLINOIS
<br></h1></b></u></b>
<b><b>Class Location: 4425 W. Irving Park Rd. Front 1, Chicago, IL 60641</b></b>
</p>
<p>
<b>ALL CLASSES ARE SUBJECT TO PRICE CHANGE AND/OR CANCELLATION WITHOUT NOTICE. WALK-INS WELCOME, BUT PREREGISTRATION IS STRONGLY RECOMMENDED IN ORDER TO RESERVE YOUR SEAT!<br>
NO REFUNDS -- CREDIT FOR FUTURE CLASSES ONLY -- CREDIT CARDS NOW ACCEPTED.<br>
CASH, CHECKS, OR MONEY ORDER MADE PAYABLE TO CHICAGOLAND DETECTIVE SERVICES</b><br>
</p>
<hr>
<p>
<h2 align="center">
<b><u>Illinois Concealed Carry - 16 Hour -- 2 day Course</b></u></h2>
<p>
Illinois Concealed Carry License program is a two day licensed program to allow persons to carry a concealed weapon<br> throughout the state of Illinois. The cost of the class is $200.00 which includes firearm usage (Glock 17 or 357 Revolver) and classroom<br> instruction. Additional fees are required in order to obtain your ICC License.<br>
<br>
<b> The fee breakdown is as follows:</b><br>
Two day, 16-hour training course: $200.00<br>
Range fees: $75.00 (payable at the range)<br>
Onsite Live Scan Fingerprinting: $60.00 (cash only)<br>
Illinois State Police Concealed Carry application fee: $150.00 (credit/debit card only)<br>
<i>OPTIONAL online ICC Application Assistance: $30.00 (cash only)</i>
<br>
<br>
Tuesday &amp; Wednesday, <b>February 28th &amp; March 1st</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Thursday &amp; Friday, <b> March 2nd &amp; 3rd</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 4th &amp; 5th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Thursday &amp; Friday, <b> March 9th &amp; 10th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 11th &amp; 12th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Tuesday &amp; Wednesday, <b> March 14th &amp; 15th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Thursday &amp; Friday, <b> March 16th &amp; 17th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 18th &amp; 19th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Thursday &amp; Friday, <b> March 23rd &amp; 24th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 25th &amp; 26th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Tuesday &amp; Wednesday, <b> March 28th &amp; 29th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Thursday &amp; Friday, <b> March 30th &amp; 31st</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
<br>
</p>
<hr>
<p>
<h2><b><u> UTAH Concealed Carry 4-Hour -- 1 day Course</u></b></h2><br>
The Utah Concealed Carry course is a one-day, 4-hour course that allows persons to carry a concealed weapon in 33+ states. This course can be easily combined with our Illinois Concealed Carry course (at a discounted price) since the course takes place immediately afterwards.  The class fee covers training, fingerprinting, and notary of application.<br>
<br>
<b> The fee breakdown is as follows:</b><br>
4-hour training course WITHOUT ICC course (cash, money order, or PayPal): $100.00<br>
<i>4-hour training course WITH ICC course (cash, money order, or PayPal): $50.00</i><br>
Passport photos (we do not provide this service): $13.00 (available at Walgreens, Costco, etc.)<br>
Utah Concealed Carry Application Fee: $47.00 (check or money order mailed with application)<br><br>
Wednesday, <b>March 1st</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br>
Friday, <b> March 3rd</b>, 6:00 PM to 10:00 PM<br>
Sunday, <b> March 5th</b>, 6:00 PM to 10:00 PM<br>
Friday, <b> March 10th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br>
Sunday, <b> March 12th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br>
Wednesday, <b> March 15th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM <br>
Friday, <b> March 17th</b>, 6:00 PM to 10:00 PM<br>
Sunday, <b> March 19th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br>
Friday, <b> March 24th</b>, 6:00 PM to 10:00 PM<br>
Sunday, <b> March 26th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br>
Wednesday, <b>March 29th</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM <br>
Friday, <b>March 31st</b>, 6:00PM to 10:00PM <br>
<br>
</p>
<hr>
<p>
<h2><b><u> Illinois Hunter Safety Course -- 2 day Course</u></b></h2><br>
We are now approved for Department of Natural Resources Hunter Safety Program. Pre-registration is required as we can only accommodate 20 students per class. For more information, call us or visit our website.  This is a free course.<br><br>
<b>March 25th and 26th</b> from 5:00 PM to 10:00 PM. <br>
</p>
<hr>
<p>
<h2><b><u> 20-HOUR UNARMED SECURITY Certificate Training Course</u></b></h2>
<br>
    The course leads to a 20-hour Basic Security Training Completion Certificate of required subjects. Cost of the session is $100.00. Additional fees are required in order to obtain your PERC card. <br><br>
<b> The fee breakdown is as follows:</b><br>
20-hour training course: $100.00 (cash, money order, or PayPal) <br>
LiveScan Fingerprinting: $60.00 (cash only)<br>
PERC card application fee (payable to IDFPR): $55.00 (check or money order mailed in with application)<br>
<i>OPTIONAL PERC card Application Assistance: $30.00 (cash only)</i><br><br>

<b><u>3-DAY OPTION: WEEKDAY CLASSES</u></b><br>
Monday, <b>March 6th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 2:00 PM<br>
