Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 11th &amp; 12th</b>, 8:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
Saturday &amp; Sunday, <b> March 25th &amp; 26th</b>, 8:00 AM -- 6:00 PM<br>
<br>
<b><u>UNARMED REFRESHER -- 1 DAY, 8-HOUR COURSE</u></b><br>

The 8-hour course allows the student to obtain an 8-hour refresher certificate to maintain employment in the unarmed security field. The cost of the program with the State of Illinois Completion Certificate is $55.00. Study guide included.
<br>
<br>
Sunday, <b>March 1st</b>, 8:00 AM -- 6:00 PM <br>
Wednesday, <b> March 8th</b>, 10:00 AM -- 6:00 PM <br>
