<p>
<b><u> <h2> 20-HOUR ARMED SECURITY Certificate Training Course</u></b></h2><br>
    The course leads to a 20-hour Completion Certificate of required subjects. The cost of the class is $100.00 which includes firearm usage (Glock 17 or 357 Revolver) &amp; classroom instruction. Additional fees are required.<br><br>
